snippet.title: Eletta - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3024120/Eletta/?utm_source=youtube_mv

While trying to escape, Eletta discovers why she was kidnapped and decides to stop it from happening to anyone else using any of the tools she finds along the way.
